data.description: Check out this brick ranch home on a cul-de-sac.   4 bedrooms, 3 baths.  Spacious living room and dining room with hardwood floors, recessed lighting and stone fireplace.  Updated kitchen with white cabinets, island, quartz countertops, and eat in area.  Owner's suite offers a full bathroom and 2 closets.  2nd bedroom with hardwood floors.  The basement offers a full bathroom with potential den and recreation area. Spacious yard with patio.   All appliances stay. Brand New furnace. Easy access to shopping, forest preserve, restaurants.  Seller is offering a $5000 closing cost credit to the buyer.
